.data-labels {
  font-size: 12px;
  text-anchor: middle;
  font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.ImageViewer {
  position: absolute;
  cursor: default;
}
.ImageViewer .svgScrollable {
  overflow: hidden;
}
.ImageViewer path.dot {
  fill: transparent;
  stroke-width: 3px;
}
.ImageViewer .notSelected {
  opacity: 0.6;
}
.ImageViewer .selected {
  opacity: 1;
}
.ImageViewer .axisGraphicsContext text {
  font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  fill: #777777;
}
.ImageViewer .axis path,
.ImageViewer .axis line {
  fill: none;
  stroke: #777777;
  shape-rendering: auto;
}
